schools.name: Spring Grove Area Senior High School

data.description: Looking for a like new home in the Spring Grove area school district?   Be sure to click on the link to see the video tour of the property.   Presenting the "Jackson XL," an impeccable two-story colonial residence featuring four bedrooms and 2.5 baths. This distinguished property marks a significant milestone as the inaugural resale in this newly established new construction community.  The residence showcases a thoughtfully designed open floor plan, highlighted by a spacious kitchen upgraded to include granite countertops. The first floor exudes sophistication with the addition of luxury vinyl plank flooring and recessed lighting, creating an inviting ambiance.  Ascending to the upper level reveals four well-appointed bedrooms, complemented by two full bathrooms. An adaptable loft area awaits, suitable for use as an office or additional living space, catering to diverse lifestyle needs. The basement, currently unfinished, provides ample storage and holds the potential for future customization to augment the living space.
